ors of the book. Early drafts of the book was used and evaluated internally within the Software Engineering Research Group at Lund University. Thus, we would like to thank the members of the group for providing feedback on different drafts of the book. In particular,we would like to thank Dr. Lars Bratthall for taking the time to review xvii

